mall whitish egg)</s></p><p class="description"><s><i>Albidovulum</i> forms rod-shaped cells that stain gram negative.</s><s>Endospores are not formed.</s><s>Slightly thermophilic.</s><s>Strictly aerobic, oxidase and catalase positive.</s><s>Facultatively halophilic or slightly halophilic.</s><s>Fatty acids are straight chained; major phospholipids are phosphatidylethanolamine and phosphatidylglycerol, ubiquinone 10 is the major respiratory quinone.</s><s>Hydrogen and reduced sulfur compounds are not used as energy sources.</s><s>Carbon dioxide is not fixed.</s><s>Chemoorganotrophic: a large number of organic compounds are used for growth.</s></p></content></protolog>